imdb.plot outline: Sadie Kaye is Miss Adventure, delivering celebrity reports from around the world. First stop: New York City. Miss Adventure hangs out with rock band Motorhead performing live at Madison Square Garden. She is supported by her 16-year old director Johnny (Dan Davies, 50).
imdb.title: Miss Adventure
plot: _Miss Adventure_ (qv) crashes a Motorhead gig at Madison Square Garden.::Barry Connell

Sadie Kaye is _Miss Adventure_ (qv), delivering celebrity reports from around the world. First stop: New York City. _Miss Adventure_ (qv) hangs out with rock band Motorhead performing live at Madison Square Garden. She is supported by her 16-year old director Johnny (Dan Davies, 50).::Funny or Die
